e models to be used, ensuring specific evaluations can be carried out.\n- **Continuity in Text Data Augmentation:** Investigate the continuity problem in text data augmentation and propose solutions to maintain the learning process.\n- **Label Preservation Techniques:** Develop advanced label preservation techniques that ensure transformations maintain class information accurately.\n- **Safety of Data Augmentation Methods:** Quantify the safety of data augmentation methods, integrating uncertainty into labels when possible.\n\n### 3. Summarization\n\nThe collective ideas revolve around improving the understanding, explainability, and safety of data augmentation techniques, particularly in the text domain. There is a need for better benchmarks and methods to address the continuity problem in text data augmentation.\n\n### 4. Formulate a New Research Idea\n\n**High-level summarized insight of a research field Machine Learning:**\nData augmentation is a critical technique for expanding training datasets, but its effectiveness in text data augmentation is not well understood. There is a need for better explainability, safety, and continuity in text data augmentation methods.\n\n**Here are the five core questions:**\n\n**[Question 1] - What is the problem?**\nHow can we improve the explainability and safety of text data augmentation techniques while maintaining the continuity of the learning process?\n\n**[Question 2] - Why is it interesting and important?**\nImproving the explainability and safety of text data augmentation will enhance the reliability and effectiveness of machine learning models. This research will provide actionable insights for the research community, leading to better data augmentation practices and more robust models.\n\n**[Question 3] - Why is it hard?**\nThe challenges include developing methods that accurately preserve class information and maintaining the continuity of the learning process. Naive approaches may fail to address these issues, leading to inaccurate models.\n\n**[Question 4] - Why hasn't it been solved before?**\nPrevious research has focused on image data augmentation, where the impact of transformations is more easily understood. The text domain presents unique challenges, such as the continuity problem, which have not been fully addressed.\n\n**[Question 5] - What are the key components of my approach and results?**\nThe proposed methodology includes developing explainable data augmentation techniques, quantifying the safety of these methods, and creating a benchmark for text data augmentation. The expected outcomes are improved data augmentation practices and more robust machine learning models.\n\nThis research idea aims to address the gaps in text data augmentation, providing valuable insights for the machine learning community."}

