**[Question 4] - Why hasn't it been solved before?**
Previous research has focused more on image data augmentation and general text data augmentation, where the impact of transformations is more visually intuitive. The continuity and explainability issues in text data augmentation for specific domains like misinformation and hate speech detection have not been thoroughly addressed due to the complexity of text semantics and the lack of standardized evaluation methods. This research aims to fill these gaps by developing novel methodologies and evaluation frameworks tailored to these domains.

**[Question 5] - What are the key components of my approach and results?**
